Description:
    Wires CafeCar into an existing Rails application. The installer mounts the
    engine under the admin namespace, creates the host ApplicationPolicy, adds
    CafeCar's controller concern, and imports the JavaScript entry points.

    It does not add gems or run Bundler. Optional features install their own
    dependencies; for example, cafe_car:sessions adds bcrypt.

Example:
    bin/rails generate cafe_car:install

    This will create:
        app/policies/application_policy.rb

    It also updates:
        config/routes.rb
        app/controllers/application_controller.rb
        app/javascript/application.js
